{"tid":486332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5G網速每秒10GB媲美光纖 政府力推最快19年有得用","createTime":"2017-12-01T17:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T19:21:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e529bd8c82c30544dc024b24e7d04933946c1e27","tid":486332,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171201/large/1512112906_4eaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171201%2Flarge%2F1512112906_4eaf.jpg&h=671dbf06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港人機不離手，為了紓緩數據流量需求問題，通訊事務管理局計劃開展5G流動服務，就工作計劃向業界進行6星期諮詢，並待在國際電信聯盟在2019年決定全球5G頻帶後，電訊商可盡早推出服務。通訊事務副總監梁仲賢指，5G技術下，數據傳送速度最快可達每秒10gb，速度媲美光纖，但強調實際速度視乎各電訊商網絡覆蓋和用量，指市民不應預期「好似拖住條無形光纖周圍走」，但網速會比4G快。<br />\n<br />\n通訊事務管理局計劃，增撥3條特定頻帶用作5G流動服務，包括26吉赫、28吉赫和3.5吉赫頻帶，當中只有28吉赫為空置頻帶，局方早前已通知數碼通及和記電訊，26吉赫頻帶內的頻率，將於2019年4月1日被撤回，會另行指配其他頻帶作替代。3.5吉赫頻帶則提供衛星服務，通訊局建議編配部分頻率用作流動服務。<br />\n通訊辧指，5G技術傳送頻率高但範圍較小，會諮詢業界，可否容許不同營辧商共用頻譜，明年將作公眾諮詢，最快2019年指配頻譜。因應技術需要，梁仲賢指政府計劃在4個地區設立400支智慧燈柱，通訊辦已爭取在燈柱預留位置，作為5G的流動基站，令網絡覆蓋更好。至於未來會否透過拍賣編配頻譜，則要視乎市場需求，底價亦會按市場價格釐定。<br />\n另外，為配合無線和流動通訊發展，通訊局今公佈新設「無線物聯網牌照」，利用920至925兆赫共用頻帶，提供無線物聯網服務，授權營辦商提供自動化、機器對機器的數據通訊，例如以物聯網裝置連接自動行駛車輛、防盜裝置、以智慧系統收集用户資料，如心跳、步速等實時資料等。<br />\n通訊局透露，現已有2家公司提出申請。發牌要求會較現時傳送者牌照為寬裕，固定費用為10萬元一年，有效期為5年，可視乎情況延長最多5年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171201/57528210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57528210&d=y6AftZrosRa1SWwQALRMaTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=80b91265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57528210&h=74221f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171201/57528210</a>"},{"pid":"ccb5dd6d67bfe2a1853a7dc54348585431f8894d","tid":486332,"uid":1807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:54:22.000Z","msg":"56k夠用啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b280e00f31b4424dcf25f33f9074861e090b3e","tid":486332,"uid":5929,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:55:11.000Z","msg":"1秒用晒成個月數據"},{"pid":"52174d7ba161c3b904e80ff3458c47582e664d94","tid":486332,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>56k夠用啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n召喚史丹利"},{"pid":"9b3690e945bedb9117632f7c8238cf9c11c97d3d","tid":486332,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1秒用晒成個月數據</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ebcafd120e015af1c865c0dbaef174c87e6d7e","tid":486332,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1秒用晒成個月數據</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0608b4bcf5542101357502a274d48b6293f8adc","tid":486332,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:08:48.000Z","msg":"幾時出返無限plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f524f9562ee5a7317c9c3b98700c61bd9e5d8f","tid":486332,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:09:56.000Z","msg":"幾快都冇撚用啦，咪又係得10gb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd70e26a20abe0a01bab82eb208bcff21c301eb0","tid":486332,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以cover左地鐵先?"},{"pid":"7101ce7a1a8f999f7880be8a669bc7aecadc6f3c","tid":486332,"uid":30169,"like":0,"disl